1
00:01:56,820 --> 00:02:02,820
=The Unexpected Marriage=

2
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:07,660
=Episode 14=

3
00:02:10,330 --> 00:02:11,170
Youmou.

4
00:02:11,450 --> 00:02:13,070
His Highness is too cautious.

5
00:02:13,330 --> 00:02:14,940
Yu has been clearly annihilated.

6
00:02:15,170 --> 00:02:17,290
Even if there are some remnants left,

7
00:02:17,290 --> 00:02:18,450
it's nothing to be afraid of.

8
00:02:18,450 --> 00:02:19,780
Why do we need to patrol?

9
00:02:20,490 --> 00:02:21,780
Look at your pouting mouth.

10
00:02:22,050 --> 00:02:23,540
It can even lift a bottle.

11
00:02:23,890 --> 00:02:25,490
Today I have an appointment with Jinyan

12
00:02:25,490 --> 00:02:27,330
to take her to see people making clay figures.

13
00:02:27,330 --> 00:02:28,770
Who made an appointment with you?

14
00:02:28,770 --> 00:02:30,360
Isn't that your own wishful thinking?

15
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,330
Did she agree?

16
00:02:31,330 --> 00:02:32,590
She didn't refuse.

17
00:02:35,610 --> 00:02:36,450
Careful.

18
00:02:54,930 --> 00:02:56,500
Who sent you here?

19
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:16,420
(Prince Qin's Mansion)

20
00:03:34,890 --> 00:03:35,730
No survivors.

21
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:37,430
There's poison behind their teeth.

22
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,080
Those captured people

23
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,360
all committed suicide.

24
00:03:41,490 --> 00:03:42,870
Judging from the pattern on the cuffs,

25
00:03:43,730 --> 00:03:44,870
they seem to be descendants of Yu.

26
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,520
Indeed.

27
00:03:48,290 --> 00:03:49,330
Has there been any movement

28
00:03:49,330 --> 00:03:50,540
at the Second Prince

29
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,540
and the Fifth Prince's mansion?

30
00:03:53,010 --> 00:03:54,240
The Second Prince

31
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,310
added some guards in his mansion.

32
00:03:56,330 --> 00:03:57,310
There's been no change.

33
00:03:57,610 --> 00:03:58,730
The Fifth Prince's mansion

34
00:03:58,730 --> 00:04:00,070
is the same like every other day.

35
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,400
But I recently heard

36
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,540
that several martial arts masters
sneaked into the city.

37
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:07,080
The detective has not yet found out

38
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,980
who's behind them.

39
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,310
Could it be that they're targeting Prince Qin?

40
00:04:12,010 --> 00:04:14,400
His Highness is about
to marry Princess Changsheng.

41
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:16,030
The Crown Prince still hasn't been decided.

42
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,760
Maybe they want to go all out.

43
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,610
Like a last-ditch attempt.

44
00:04:19,610 --> 00:04:20,500
Who are they?

45
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,500
The Second Prince and the Fifth Prince
want to compete for the throne.

46
00:04:24,090 --> 00:04:25,670
But if they have
a private relationship with Yu,

47
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,380
that's a capital crime.

48
00:04:27,650 --> 00:04:28,490
Your Highness.

49
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:29,600
Youmou.

50
00:04:29,970 --> 00:04:31,630
Investigate the background of these bandits

51
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:34,090
and the martial artists
who sneaked into the city a few days ago.

52
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,400
If there is any news,

53
00:04:35,650 --> 00:04:36,490
report to me immediately.

54
00:04:36,730 --> 00:04:37,570
Yes.

55
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,280
Youyong.

56
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:40,660
Increase the guards at Huadeng Pavilion.

57
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:42,900
Tell Changsheng not to leave the house
for the next few days.

58
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,870
Make sure to keep her safe.

59
00:04:45,490 --> 00:04:46,820
There can't be any mistakes.

60
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,400
Yes.

61
00:05:04,930 --> 00:05:05,770
Your Highness.

62
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:08,320
His Highness has ordered,
no one is allowed to leave the house

63
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,220
without a necessary reason.

64
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:11,460
Everyone including me?

65
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,610
Though you haven't gotten married yet,

66
00:05:13,610 --> 00:05:14,580
it does include you.

67
00:05:16,610 --> 00:05:17,870
What happened?

68
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,360
We are only executing the order.

69
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,230
We don't know anything else.

70
00:05:23,610 --> 00:05:24,680
Do you have

71
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,560
some exceptions?

72
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,820
That requires His Highness's token.

73
00:05:29,610 --> 00:05:31,500
What if I must leave the house
without the token?

74
00:05:33,170 --> 00:05:34,930
We're ordered to guard this place.

75
00:05:34,930 --> 00:05:36,590
- Please don't make things difficult for us.
- Okay, okay.

76
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,500
I'll go back to my room, okay?

77
00:05:45,170 --> 00:05:46,770
Would you like to eat some fruit?

78
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,820
No appetite.

79
00:05:49,090 --> 00:05:50,240
How about we

80
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,120
play the shuttlecock?

81
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,020
My feet are sore.

82
00:05:52,970 --> 00:05:53,810
Then

83
00:05:53,850 --> 00:05:54,880
we can practice writing.

84
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,110
I'm sleepy.

85
00:05:57,530 --> 00:06:00,200
Your Highness, don't be so listless.

86
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:02,110
You can get up and talk to us.

87
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,040
Your Highness, where are you going?

88
00:06:06,490 --> 00:06:07,500
I'm going to find Lv Jing.

89
00:06:07,730 --> 00:06:08,790
I want to go out.

90
00:06:09,490 --> 00:06:10,340
Your Highness.

91
00:06:10,650 --> 00:06:11,580
Prince Qin

92
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,730
is your future husband.

93
00:06:13,730 --> 00:06:15,050
Whatever happens,

94
00:06:15,050 --> 00:06:16,500
you must control your temper.

95
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:18,730
Your Highness.

96
00:06:18,730 --> 00:06:19,730
Be careful with your words.

97
00:06:19,730 --> 00:06:20,750
Be careful with your actions.

98
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,940
It's been so many days.

99
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,970
Why are you following me so strictly?

100
00:06:55,970 --> 00:06:57,580
It's like I'm running away from marriage.

101
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,260
I don't believe it.

102
00:07:00,730 --> 00:07:01,880
The more you don't let me leave here,

103
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,070
the more I want to leave here.

104
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,670
Chase her. Your Highness.

105
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:13,340
(Pen and Ink)

106
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,630
It's so frustrating
not being able to leave the house.

107
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,490
Don't be frustrated, Your Highness.

108
00:07:18,490 --> 00:07:19,760
Come down soon.

109
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,870
Don't fall.

110
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,970
I came up with great difficulty.

111
00:07:22,970 --> 00:07:24,360
I won't go down simply because you ask me to.

112
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,530
It's not that easy.

113
00:07:25,530 --> 00:07:26,490
Your Highness.

114
00:07:26,490 --> 00:07:27,560
As long as His Highness wants,

115
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,800
even a fly can't fly out of here.

116
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,880
- Yes.
- You are the fly.

117
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:32,900
What kind of metaphor is that?

118
00:07:33,410 --> 00:07:34,440
Spring is in full swing.

119
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,580
You can't lock me up.

120
00:07:36,410 --> 00:07:37,410
Have you heard the poem?

121
00:07:37,410 --> 00:07:39,190
As spring cannot be kept in a house yard,

122
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,410
a red apricot bloom...

123
00:07:40,410 --> 00:07:42,310
Creeps over the wall.

124
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:45,090
Do you want to climb over the wall?

125
00:07:45,090 --> 00:07:46,310
I don't.

126
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,520
We were wrong.

127
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:49,120
But please come down now.

128
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,140
If you get hurt,

129
00:07:50,490 --> 00:07:51,630
His Highness will blame us.

130
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,720
I don't.

131
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:54,580
I want to bask in the sun here.

132
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,640
Careful.

133
00:08:03,970 --> 00:08:04,810
Bask in the sun?

134
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,310
Next time you have this plan,

135
00:08:06,530 --> 00:08:07,870
ask me to join you.

136
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,640
Never mind.

137
00:08:12,090 --> 00:08:13,630
It seems that basking in the sun

138
00:08:13,930 --> 00:08:15,110
is pretty dangerous.

139
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,460
I'm going back.

140
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,200
Your Highness.

141
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,280
I'm afraid

142
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,510
Her Highness

143
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,980
will still think about going out.

144
00:08:34,770 --> 00:08:36,310
Should I send more people

145
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,440
to guard her?

146
00:08:37,530 --> 00:08:38,370
For this kind of thing,

147
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:39,980
the more you don't let her do it,

148
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:41,940
the more she wants to do it.

149
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:44,030
- Then...
- It's better to divert the flood

150
00:08:44,650 --> 00:08:45,700
rather than blocking it.

151
00:08:53,130 --> 00:08:54,510
His Highness is knowledgeable.

152
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,560
Youmou.

153
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,280
Flood?

154
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,560
What does it mean?

155
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,940
Where is the flood?

156
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,070
Where is the flood?

157
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,820
I asked you to read more books.

158
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,190
"Strategies to Tame the Flood".

159
00:09:11,580 --> 00:09:14,100
(Huadeng Pavilion)

160
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,320
Your Highness.

161
00:09:17,890 --> 00:09:18,730
Your Highness.

162
00:09:18,770 --> 00:09:19,740
Have you got the token?

163
00:09:22,010 --> 00:09:22,930
Why is your face

164
00:09:22,930 --> 00:09:23,980
so red?

165
00:09:26,050 --> 00:09:26,890
Is it red?

166
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,520
Maybe

167
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,340
it's because I just ran back.

168
00:09:31,770 --> 00:09:34,030
Exercise makes people hot.

169
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:37,600
Never mind. Never mind.

170
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:39,510
Look what this is.

171
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,740
His Highness didn't find it out?

172
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,100
Of course.

173
00:09:43,530 --> 00:09:44,720
- So what if he's an old fox?
- A mouse.

174
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,440
While the priest climbs a post,
the devil climbs ten.

175
00:09:46,650 --> 00:09:48,220
I stole the token after all.

176
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,840
It didn't take much effort to get it.

177
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:52,740
Your Highness, you got a fake token.

178
00:09:53,010 --> 00:09:54,170
What fake token?

179
00:09:54,170 --> 00:09:55,010
This...

180
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:57,780
(Pure Like Orchids)

181
00:10:00,290 --> 00:10:01,190
Lv Jing.

182
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:03,430
You old fox.

183
00:10:05,410 --> 00:10:06,650
The cylinder is too slippery.

184
00:10:06,650 --> 00:10:07,550
Little mouse,

185
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:08,940
let's wait and see.

186
00:10:16,010 --> 00:10:18,220
But why doesn't he let me leave the house?

187
00:10:20,770 --> 00:10:21,720
Is it possible

188
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,770
that there are some

189
00:10:22,770 --> 00:10:23,800
monsters

190
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:24,940
or ghosts outside?

191
00:10:25,290 --> 00:10:26,580
What happened

192
00:10:27,050 --> 00:10:28,270
to make him so cautious?

193
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,390
His Highness has always been thoughtful.

194
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,010
I guess he's doing this

195
00:10:32,010 --> 00:10:33,860
for your safety.

196
00:10:34,130 --> 00:10:35,220
If you really want to know,

197
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,820
just ask him directly.

198
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,160
Never mind.

199
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,580
I have a way without asking him.

200
00:10:40,890 --> 00:10:42,370
Your Highness, go change your clothes.

201
00:10:43,010 --> 00:10:43,850
Go.

202
00:10:50,930 --> 00:10:52,940
Have another drink.

203
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,910
You can't refuse.

204
00:10:55,890 --> 00:10:58,200
Your Highness, during our shift,

205
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,560
we can't drink alcohol.

206
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,430
What are you afraid of?

207
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,250
If His Highness blames you,

208
00:11:02,250 --> 00:11:03,100
let him come to me.

209
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,560
His Highness

210
00:11:06,050 --> 00:11:07,700
definitely won't blame you.

211
00:11:08,130 --> 00:11:08,970
But

212
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,720
he will punish us.

213
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,560
Then,

214
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:15,250
if you can answer my question,

215
00:11:15,250 --> 00:11:16,980
you can avoid drinking this wine.

216
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,720
What do you

217
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,860
want to know?

218
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,340
Recently, is there

219
00:11:24,650 --> 00:11:25,700
something big going on out there?

220
00:11:30,410 --> 00:11:31,250
Drink.

221
00:11:31,410 --> 00:11:32,250
Drink.

222
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:34,250
Our mansion is strengthening guard

223
00:11:34,250 --> 00:11:35,310
because of this matter?

224
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,340
They're coming for me?

225
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:40,390
Your Highness.

226
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,910
You have to ask His Highness yourself.

227
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,090
We are just following orders

228
00:11:45,090 --> 00:11:46,190
to protect you.

229
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,880
His Highness

230
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:49,820
didn't let us reveal anything else.

231
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,030
Not reveal.

232
00:11:51,250 --> 00:11:52,460
I want you to explain the details.

233
00:11:53,370 --> 00:11:54,390
If you don't tell me,

234
00:11:54,890 --> 00:11:56,430
you need to drink more.

235
00:12:00,770 --> 00:12:01,610
Come on.

236
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,040
Come on.

237
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,360
If you still don't say,

238
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,960
I'll go tell His Highness

239
00:12:12,050 --> 00:12:13,440
that you drank alcohol while on duty.

240
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,620
You will be punished too.

241
00:12:15,290 --> 00:12:16,130
Your Highness.

242
00:12:16,250 --> 00:12:17,770
You forced us to drink.

243
00:12:17,770 --> 00:12:18,770
Yes.

244
00:12:18,770 --> 00:12:20,070
I forced you to drink?

245
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:22,070
Who saw it?

246
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,740
I didn't.

247
00:12:24,250 --> 00:12:25,130
Who can prove it?

248
00:12:25,130 --> 00:12:26,310
No one can prove it.

249
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:27,440
You...

250
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,680
So Youyong and Youmou

251
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:30,080
drank alcohol while on duty,

252
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,200
and I caught them.

253
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,130
They even falsely accused me.

254
00:12:33,050 --> 00:12:34,620
Shenxing, note it down.

255
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:35,760
Let's go find His Highness.

256
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:36,600
Okay.

257
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:37,520
Well...

258
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:40,310
Don't talk nonsense.

259
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:43,270
His Highness is afraid that
Her Highness will worry,

260
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:45,620
so he did not allow us to talk.

261
00:12:47,250 --> 00:12:48,960
I didn't say anything.

262
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:51,150
Isn't it the assassination incident
some days ago?

263
00:12:52,130 --> 00:12:53,070
Assassination?

264
00:12:55,370 --> 00:12:56,980
Your Highness, what about them?

265
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,040
They will sober up.

266
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,250
What to do now?

267
00:13:06,250 --> 00:13:07,200
Take a cold shower

268
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,270
to get rid of the smell of alcohol.

269
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:10,460
We still have to check for the assassin later.

270
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:11,680
Let's go.

271
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,680
Go.

272
00:13:19,860 --> 00:13:21,820
(Equalling Men of Virtue)

273
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:22,540
In recent days,

274
00:13:22,540 --> 00:13:24,990
the secret guards have checked the situation
in various places in the city.

275
00:13:24,990 --> 00:13:27,230
The people involved in the assassination
have also been eliminated.

276
00:13:27,290 --> 00:13:28,860
There is no accident in the city at present.

277
00:13:31,170 --> 00:13:32,010
What about Her Highness?

278
00:13:32,170 --> 00:13:33,230
Her Highness

279
00:13:33,370 --> 00:13:34,740
have been quiet these days.

280
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,930
After asking us last time,

281
00:13:36,930 --> 00:13:38,390
she doesn't want to leave the house now.

282
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,160
It's late.

283
00:13:42,800 --> 00:13:43,640
Let's go see her tomorrow.

284
00:13:44,050 --> 00:13:44,890
Okay.

285
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,980
Jinyan, I caught two more.

286
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:50,640
Look.

287
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,050
(Youlan Pavilion)
How long do we have to wait

288
00:13:53,050 --> 00:13:54,580
to catch a hundred of them?

