00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,760
Miss, you have good taste.

400
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:51,820
Is it beautiful?

401
00:17:52,890 --> 00:17:54,480
Which one do you like?

402
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,520
This one.

403
00:17:55,520 --> 00:17:56,850
- OK.
