00:18:40,930 --> 00:18:42,180
Look at your expression.

417
00:18:43,610 --> 00:18:45,470
It's just like this mask.

418
00:18:47,890 --> 00:18:49,140
What did you promise me?

419
00:18:49,410 --> 00:18:50,280
Didn't we agree to...

420
00:18:50,280 --> 00:18:51,240
Follow you closely

