444
00:19:37,810 --> 00:19:38,950
I always think about

445
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:41,100
what I can do for our people.

446
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:43,920
I will try to find a way

447
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,810
