452
00:19:59,280 --> 00:20:00,120
Okay.

453
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:02,380
Take your things and wait in the carriage.

454
00:20:02,610 --> 00:20:03,450
- We'll meet up in a bit.
- Yes.

455
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:05,280
Okay.

456
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,080
Let's go.

457
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:11,960
Please take it.

458
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:12,800
Thanks.

459
00:20:12,890 --> 00:20:13,900
Come again.

460
00:20:14,930 --> 00:20:16,030
Sugarcoated haws.

461
00:20:16,760 --> 00:20:18,140
Delicious sugarcoated haws.

462
00:20:23,090 --> 00:20:23,930
