465
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,620
Wait until life becomes peaceful,

466
00:20:31,930 --> 00:20:32,820
I'll come with you often.

467
00:20:35,410 --> 00:20:36,250
Follow me.

468
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:38,840
Buy some.

469
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:53,990
So beautiful.

470
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:01,420
Previously in Fuyu,

471
00:21:01,890 --> 00:21:03,090
we often heard

472
00:21:03,090 --> 00:21:04,370
how prosperous Great Tang is.

473
00:21:04,370 --> 00:21:05,230
After today's visit,

474
00:21:05,320 --> 00:21:06,280
it surely lives up to its name.

475
00:21:07,090 --> 00:21:07,950
I'm thinking

476
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:09,900
for the people to live and work in peace,

477
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:11,580
the country needs to be stable

478
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:13,180
and the world peaceful.

479
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:14,950
We were born in the royal family.

480
00:21:15,370 --> 00:21:17,420
So we should think what the people think,

481
00:21:17,850 --> 00:21:19,230
and worry what the people worry.

482
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:21,270
If the people in Great Tang and Fuyu

483
00:21:21,850 --> 00:21:23,650
