484
00:21:23,650 --> 00:21:24,790
the prosperous times now

485
00:21:25,370 --> 00:21:26,730
can be passed down for thousands of years.

486
00:21:30,480 --> 00:21:31,860
Why did you suddenly think of this?

487
00:21:35,240 --> 00:21:36,950
Fuyu's market is also very lively.

488
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:38,370
Nowadays,

489
00:21:38,370 --> 00:21:39,620
on the streets of Great Tang,

490
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:41,410
watching the busy traffic,

491
00:21:41,410 --> 00:21:42,570
the hustle and bustle of crowds,

492
00:21:42,570 --> 00:21:43,420
I just feel

493
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:45,650
indescribably

494
00:21:45,650 --> 00:21:46,900
moved.

495
00:21:47,610 --> 00:21:48,450
Just like

496
00:21:48,850 --> 00:21:49,820
people in the world

497
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:52,380
should live happily and peacefully like this.

498
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:53,990
Of course, all this

499
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,280
still depends on Great Tang

500
00:21:55,280 --> 00:21:57,070
protecting the people on this land.

501
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,380
Being in the right position,

502
00:21:58,650 --> 00:22:00,230
we must seek happiness for the people.

503
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:02,270
This has always been my motto.

504
00:22:04,570 --> 00:22:06,310
The people of Great Tang are my responsibility.

505
00:22:06,610 --> 00:22:07,750
Now Fuyu is too.

506
00:22:08,610 --> 00:22:10,130
I will spare no effort

507
00:22:10,130 --> 00:22:12,580
to provide a better life for all.

508
00:22:14,610 --> 00:22:15,620
You did a great job.

509
00:22:15,850 --> 00:22:17,340
Taste this as a reward.

