511
00:22:30,610 --> 00:22:31,860
It fell.

512
00:22:32,130 --> 00:22:33,380
I'll buy a new one.

513
00:22:50,130 --> 00:22:50,970
Young Lady.

514
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:52,100
Where are you going?

