531
00:24:30,130 --> 00:24:31,140
Let's go back home.

532
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:35,940
(Prince Qin's Mansion)

533
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:41,140
Have the assassins in the market been found?

534
00:24:41,650 --> 00:24:42,660
After the carriage was hit,

535
00:24:42,930 --> 00:24:44,680
