536
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:46,240
worrying about your and Her Highness's safety.

537
00:24:46,240 --> 00:24:48,470
Then these assassins
blended into the crowd and escaped.

538
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:49,560
But...

539
00:24:50,610 --> 00:24:51,450
But what?

540
00:24:51,650 --> 00:24:53,810
But we examined the body of the dead assassin.

541
00:24:53,810 --> 00:24:55,170
The pattern on his cuffs

542
00:24:55,170 --> 00:24:56,750
