545
00:25:01,090 --> 00:25:01,990
It's a scar.

546
00:25:02,280 --> 00:25:03,120
This scar

547
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:05,100
was caused by a knife cut later.

548
00:25:05,760 --> 00:25:07,310
After careful examination, we found

549
00:25:07,520 --> 00:25:08,930
the scar is to cover up the slave imprint

550
00:25:08,930 --> 00:25:10,340
peculiar to the royal family.

551
00:25:10,850 --> 00:25:12,680
Same as you guessed before,

552
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,090
it should be done by someone from the palace.

553
00:25:14,130 --> 00:25:15,610
Although the back has been scratched,

554
00:25:15,610 --> 00:25:16,950
we can vaguely recognize

555
00:25:17,370 --> 00:25:18,210
this pattern

556
00:25:18,520 --> 00:25:19,660
is the totem of the Second Prince.

557
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,040
Lv Hou.

558
00:25:23,650 --> 00:25:24,580
Keep investigating.

559
00:25:25,370 --> 00:25:26,420
You mean...

560
00:25:26,760 --> 00:25:28,510
