564
00:25:34,760 --> 00:25:35,600
Yes.

565
00:25:36,330 --> 00:25:38,200
Your Highness, let's apply the medicine.

566
00:25:38,200 --> 00:25:39,040
You guys can leave.

567
00:25:41,930 --> 00:25:43,180
It's a minor injury, not serious.

568
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:54,860
You took me out of the mansion.

569
00:25:55,170 --> 00:25:57,070
I guess you had confirmed it was safe.

570
00:25:57,650 --> 00:25:59,270
But we encountered an assassination again.

571
00:25:59,810 --> 00:26:01,810
I'm afraid the last assassination

572
00:26:01,810 --> 00:26:03,030
