00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:11,340
I didn't think carefully.

578
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,200
I just came to Great Tang

579
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:14,340
and don't know your situation.

580
00:26:14,610 --> 00:26:15,820
I even clamored to go out,

581
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:17,580
caused you trouble,

582
00:26:18,570 --> 00:26:19,660
and hurt you.

583
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:22,560
Sorry.

584
00:26:22,890 --> 00:26:23,900
Why bother saying this?

585
00:26:24,850 --> 00:26:25,860
Training a desperado

586
00:26:26,090 --> 00:26:27,550
takes three to five years.

587
00:26:28,040 --> 00:26:29,180
These people were well prepared.

588
00:26:29,810 --> 00:26:31,660
It's only a matter of time
before they take action.

589
00:26:33,280 --> 00:26:34,750
You don't have to take it to heart.

590
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:38,140
But you still got hurt.

591
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:40,880
Don't worry.

592
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:43,140
I will adapt to the situation here
as soon as possible.

593
00:26:44,610 --> 00:26:45,450
So

594
00:26:45,890 --> 00:26:47,180
no matter what happens to you,

595
00:26:47,650 --> 00:26:48,860
you can tell me.

596
00:26:49,520 --> 00:26:50,510
You don't need to be

597
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:51,990
extremely cautious for me.

598
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:54,030
I don't want it

599
00:26:54,520 --> 00:26:56,340
that you'll always stand in front of me.

600
00:26:58,410 --> 00:26:59,340
You are good enough.

601
00:26:59,650 --> 00:27:00,550
Not enough.

602
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,710
You want me to trust you.

603
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,790
I hope you can trust me too.

604
00:27:05,090 --> 00:27:06,140
We will be each other's

605
00:27:06,370 --> 00:27:07,420
most powerful ally.

606
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:19,820
Have you heard that Prince Qin got injured?

607
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:21,130
What?

608
00:27:21,130 --> 00:27:22,410
The invincible Prince Qin

609
00:27:22,410 --> 00:27:23,760
was injured in Luojing?

610
00:27:23,760 --> 00:27:24,890
That's right.

611
00:27:24,890 --> 00:27:27,030
This is a hot topic among the public recently.

612
00:27:27,650 --> 00:27:29,280
I heard that Prince Qin was injured

613
00:27:29,280 --> 00:27:31,170
because of the future Princess Consort Qin.

614
00:27:31,170 --> 00:27:32,090
They're at odds?

615
00:27:32,090 --> 00:27:32,930
No.

616
00:27:33,090 --> 00:27:34,800
It is said that the Princess of Fuyu

617
00:27:34,800 --> 00:27:35,850
is a witch.

618
00:27:35,850 --> 00:27:38,000
All the men who admire her
will have a bad ending.

619
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,410
That's why Prince Qin was injured.

620
00:27:39,410 --> 00:27:41,240
This matter has long been known
to everyone in Fuyu.

621
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:42,650
Only Prince Qin is still kept in the dark.

622
00:27:42,650 --> 00:27:44,610
This sounds a bit unbelievable.

623
00:27:44,610 --> 00:27:45,860
Right.

624
00:27:47,760 --> 00:27:49,810
Let's continue from last time.

625
00:27:49,810 --> 00:27:51,370
Last time we said

626
00:27:51,370 --> 00:27:53,070
the lone star

627
00:27:53,610 --> 00:27:55,340
happened to fall

628
00:27:55,890 --> 00:27:58,710
into a family in Fuyu.

629
00:27:59,170 --> 00:28:00,370
This family

630
00:28:00,370 --> 00:28:02,340
is not an ordinary family.

631
00:28:02,810 --> 00:28:05,550
It's a prince of Fuyu.

632
00:28:06,370 --> 00:28:07,510
And this child

633
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:10,470
became Fuyu's princess.

634
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:13,340
Because the lone star

635
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:15,470
lives in the princess's body,

636
00:28:15,930 --> 00:28:16,770
so

637
00:28:17,090 --> 00:28:20,040
since the birth of this child,

638
00:28:20,040 --> 00:28:24,760
there has been no peace in the whole mansion.

639
00:28:24,760 --> 00:28:26,420
Who are you talking about?

640
00:28:26,930 --> 00:28:28,310
- I'm going to destroy your tavern.
- You...

641
00:28:31,620 --> 00:28:34,100
(Huadeng Pavilion)

642
00:28:34,130 --> 00:28:35,170
Your Highness.

643
00:28:35,170 --> 00:28:36,270
What happened?

644
00:28:39,570 --> 00:28:41,090
Who is so bold

645
00:28:41,090 --> 00:28:42,100
as to bully my maids?

646
00:28:42,650 --> 00:28:43,490
Wait and see.

647
00:28:44,570 --> 00:28:46,130
No one bullied us.

648
00:28:46,130 --> 00:28:47,280
Someone bullied you.

649
00:28:47,280 --> 00:28:48,520
We didn't fight.

650
00:28:48,520 --> 00:28:49,820
We went to smash up the tavern.

651
00:28:50,090 --> 00:28:51,930
So you guys bullied others.

652
00:28:51,930 --> 00:28:53,000
I just thought

653
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:55,030
my maids wouldn't get bullied.

654
00:28:55,370 --> 00:28:56,570
Your Highness.

655
00:28:56,570 --> 00:28:57,930
Is this the point?

656
00:28:57,930 --> 00:28:59,470
The point is that someone bullied you.

657
00:29:00,440 --> 00:29:01,280
Tell me.

658
00:29:01,610 --> 00:29:02,790
What on earth happened?

659
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:05,900
They spread rumors

660
00:29:06,130 --> 00:29:08,180
that you are the reincarnation of a lone star.

661
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:09,890
You'll affect the fortune of Great Tang.

662
00:29:09,890 --> 00:29:11,140
(The rumor has spread to Great Tang.)

663
00:29:12,090 --> 00:29:13,750
(It seems someone did it on purpose.)

664
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:14,860
I see.

665
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:16,830
Don't worry, I know what I'm doing.

666
00:29:25,520 --> 00:29:27,280
The horse got crazy?

667
00:29:27,280 --> 00:29:28,120
Father.

668
00:29:28,650 --> 00:29:29,490
Actually,

669
00:29:30,090 --> 00:29:32,070
everyone knows it now.

670
00:29:32,280 --> 00:29:34,100
Although I don't quite believe it,

671
00:29:34,610 --> 00:29:36,440
the recent events

672
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:38,480
are worrying indeed.

673
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:39,610
Lv Jing's carriage

674
00:29:39,610 --> 00:29:41,330
was rolling along the road.

675
00:29:41,330 --> 00:29:43,470
How could the mad horse

676
00:29:43,890 --> 00:29:45,100
bump into it?

677
00:29:47,090 --> 00:29:48,900
Fortunately, nothing happened.

678
00:29:49,650 --> 00:29:51,180
But the strangest thing is

679
00:29:51,650 --> 00:29:54,370
why did the horse suddenly go crazy?

680
00:29:54,370 --> 00:29:55,270
Right.

681
00:29:55,890 --> 00:29:59,170
Why did the horse suddenly go crazy?

682
00:29:59,170 --> 00:30:00,570
Yes, Father.

683
00:30:00,570 --> 00:30:02,240
This is the crux of the matter.

684
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,410
The merchants have said

685
00:30:03,410 --> 00:30:05,510
this horse is usually very docile.

686
00:30:05,760 --> 00:30:07,440
It never lost its temper.

687
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:09,690
But how come it suddenly went crazy

688
00:30:09,690 --> 00:30:11,030
after seeing Lv Jing's carriage?

689
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:12,510
This situation

690
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,550
only has one explanation.

691
00:30:15,280 --> 00:30:16,180
That is...

692
00:30:17,370 --> 00:30:18,860
What is that?

693
00:30:19,930 --> 00:30:21,860
The rumor is true.

694
00:30:22,850 --> 00:30:24,210
The Princess of Fuyu

695
00:30:24,210 --> 00:30:26,580
is really the reincarnation of the lone star.

696
00:30:29,650 --> 00:30:30,490
Son.

697
00:30:30,610 --> 00:30:31,950
You need to be responsible

698
00:30:32,760 --> 00:30:34,990
with what you say.

699
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:38,100
I said the wrong thing again.

700
00:30:38,370 --> 00:30:39,210
Father.

701
00:30:39,330 --> 00:30:40,410
I spoke without thing

702
00:30:40,410 --> 00:30:41,420
because I cared too much.

703
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:43,680
What if it's true?

704
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:44,520
Father.

705
00:30:45,090 --> 00:30:46,760
Great Tang's fortune

706
00:30:46,760 --> 00:30:49,270
allows no slip-ups.

707
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:51,040
Fine.

708
00:30:51,810 --> 00:30:52,650
Someone,

709
00:30:53,330 --> 00:30:54,180
summon

710
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:55,710
Princess Changsheng.

711
00:30:57,090 --> 00:30:58,140
His Majesty wants to see me.

712
00:30:59,130 --> 00:31:01,510
Why does he suddenly want to see you?

713
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:04,790
I'm afraid the rumors about me recently

714
00:31:05,130 --> 00:31:07,000
were spread by someone on purpose.

715
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:08,090
What to do then?

716
00:31:08,090 --> 00:31:09,680
If it is true as you said,

717
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:11,610
you can't go to the palace.

718
00:31:11,610 --> 00:31:13,930
If I don't go, it means
I have a guilty conscience.

719
00:31:13,930 --> 00:31:16,380
Once you go, you might not come back.

720
00:31:17,330 --> 00:31:18,750
This happened because of me.

721
00:31:19,090 --> 00:31:20,080
His Highness is busy.

722
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:21,070
Don't tell him yet.

723
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:22,510
Your Highness.

724
00:31:23,330 --> 00:31:24,170
Don't worry.

725
00:31:24,520 --> 00:31:25,510
I'll try to solve it.

726
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:33,520
I heard

727
00:31:33,810 --> 00:31:35,090
Fuyu

728
00:31:35,090 --> 00:31:37,580
is good at growing flowers and plants.

729
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:39,280
Changsheng.

730
00:31:39,650 --> 00:31:42,790
Look at how my flowers are growing.

731
00:31:43,850 --> 00:31:46,550
It's not appropriate to plant

732
00:31:46,660 --> 00:31:47,600
lilac and daffodil together.

733
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:50,720
Why is that?

734
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:52,820
Different flowers have different habits.

735
00:31:53,090 --> 00:31:55,040
Lilac likes plenty of sunshine

736
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:56,090
and has strong shade-resistance.

737
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:57,610
Daffodil

738
00:31:57,610 --> 00:31:58,960
prefers warm and humid climates.

739
00:31:58,960 --> 00:32:00,520
And it needs sufficient rainfall.

740
00:32:00,520 --> 00:32:02,410
Two seemingly unrelated plants

741
00:32:02,410 --> 00:32:04,720
will hurt each other when planted together.

742
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:06,340
Everything in the world is interdependent.

743
00:32:06,570 --> 00:32:07,790
This is natural law.

744
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:10,660
If the two plants are grown separately,

745
00:32:10,930 --> 00:32:12,140
I guess it will be better.

746
00:32:12,520 --> 00:32:14,580
Even nature has laws.

747
00:32:15,370 --> 00:32:17,100
What about human beings?

748
00:32:21,280 --> 00:32:22,370
Your Majesty.

749
00:32:22,370 --> 00:32:24,400
I have something to confess.

750
00:32:24,420 --> 00:32:25,270
Go ahead.

751
00:32:25,280 --> 00:32:26,900
When I was in Fuyu,

752
00:32:27,170 --> 00:32:29,270
it was once rumored that I was a lone star.

753
00:32:29,760 --> 00:32:31,030
Therefore, in Fuyu,

754
00:32:31,330 --> 00:32:32,370
no men

755
00:32:32,370 --> 00:32:33,370
wanted to marry me.

756
00:32:33,370 --> 00:32:35,270
So you mean

757
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:37,030
the peace-making marriage

758
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:39,040
is not what you want?

759
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:40,030
Quite the contrary.

760
00:32:40,330 --> 00:32:42,230
The marriage was initiated by me.

761
00:32:42,480 --> 00:32:45,000
Although I don't care about the rumor,

762
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:46,520
since I'm married to Great Tang,

763
00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:48,410
naturally, I don't want these unfounded rumors

764
00:32:48,410 --> 00:32:49,660
to affect Prince Jing.

765
00:32:52,130 --> 00:32:53,230
Get up.

766
00:32:53,720 --> 00:32:56,180
Today we're appreciating the flowers.

767
00:32:56,410 --> 00:32:58,030
Why did you talk about this?

768
00:33:00,650 --> 00:33:01,810
Your Majesty.

769
00:33:01,810 --> 00:33:03,470
The envoy from An
presented a letter of credence.

770
00:33:03,630 --> 00:33:04,550
Please read it, Your Majesty.

771
00:33:10,850 --> 00:33:11,760
This...

772
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:14,340
An is becoming bolder.

773
00:33:14,760 --> 00:33:16,370
They wrote the letter

774
00:33:16,370 --> 00:33:18,510
in their own native language.

775
00:33:19,090 --> 00:33:19,930
Who can understand

776
00:33:20,090 --> 00:33:21,820
this letter?

777
00:33:23,170 --> 00:33:24,010
Wan.

778
00:33:24,330 --> 00:33:25,820
Take a look for me.

779
00:33:30,330 --> 00:33:32,820
I could read An's language.

780
00:33:33,330 --> 00:33:35,340
It's just this letter...

781
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:38,850
I heard that An recently
made changes to their language.

782
00:33:38,850 --> 00:33:40,000
I can't fully

783
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:41,660
understand this letter.

784
00:33:42,410 --> 00:33:43,790
Then leave it to the Ministry of Rites.

785
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:45,080
Your Majesty.

786
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:46,470
Could I

787
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:47,990
have a look?

788
00:33:48,370 --> 00:33:49,210
You?

789
00:33:49,930 --> 00:33:51,850
Even my aunt can't read it.

790
00:33:51,850 --> 00:33:53,240
Can you understand it?

791
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:55,230
You'd better not make a fool of yourself.

792
00:33:56,170 --> 00:33:57,610
You have to

793
00:33:57,610 --> 00:33:59,230
let me read it first

794
00:33:59,450 --> 00:34:00,750
to know whether I'll make a fool of myself.

795
00:34:01,130 --> 00:34:02,180
Please, Your Majesty.

796
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:04,420
Then take a look.

797
00:34:10,560 --> 00:34:11,400
Your Majesty.

798
00:34:11,640 --> 00:34:12,890
In this letter,

799
00:34:12,890 --> 00:34:14,300
the intention is to pay respects to you.

800
00:34:14,770 --> 00:34:16,770
It's mentioned that
at the border between the two countries,

801
00:34:16,770 --> 00:34:18,520
there have been bandits
causing chaos occasionally.

802
00:34:18,850 --> 00:34:20,930
But An has sent troops to quell it.

803
00:34:20,930 --> 00:34:22,070
Please rest assured, Your Majesty.

804
00:34:23,890 --> 00:34:25,000
At the end of the letter,

805
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:26,300
they used very respectful words.

806
00:34:26,730 --> 00:34:27,830
They mentioned Your Majesty

807
00:34:28,370 --> 00:34:29,640
is quite busy,

808
00:34:29,640 --> 00:34:31,140
and asked you to take care of your health.

809
00:34:33,410 --> 00:34:34,250
You...

810
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,870
How can you

811
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,140
understand this letter?

812
00:34:39,250 --> 00:34:41,660
Yeah, I'm curious too.

813
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:43,370
You can even

814
00:34:43,370 --> 00:34:45,040
recognize

815
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:46,370
such complicated

816
00:34:46,370 --> 00:34:47,220
honorifics.

817
00:34:47,520 --> 00:34:48,360
Your Majesty.

818
00:34:48,520 --> 00:34:49,410
I've always liked

819
00:34:49,410 --> 00:34:50,910
to study the language of different countries.

820
00:34:51,240 --> 00:34:52,640
Among them, the written and spoken language

821
00:34:52,640 --> 00:34:54,370
of An are not the same,

822
00:34:54,370 --> 00:34:55,580
so there are frequent changes.

823
00:34:55,810 --> 00:34:57,040
Out of curiosity,

824
00:34:57,040 --> 00:34:58,780
I paid special attention to An's language.

825
00:34:59,210 --> 00:35:02,140
I showed myself up
in front of Princess Royal and Your Majesty.

826
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:05,830
You're too modest.

827
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:06,960
Wan.

828
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:08,140
In this regard,

829
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:10,040
you've met your match.

830
00:35:10,040 --> 00:35:11,220
You're right, Brother.

831
00:35:11,890 --> 00:35:13,520
Being proficient in languages,

832
00:35:13,520 --> 00:35:15,160
the Princess of Fuyu

833
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:16,780
does have some skills.

834
00:35:17,040 --> 00:35:18,830
I'm flattered.

835
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:34,950
It's been a tiring trip.

836
00:35:35,250 --> 00:35:36,350
Especially Princess Changsheng.

837
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:37,550
With all the explanations,

838
00:35:37,890 --> 00:35:39,120
you must be thirsty.

839
00:35:39,120 --> 00:35:39,960
Hou.

840
00:35:41,640 --> 00:35:43,910
Why don't you pour a glass of water for her?

841
00:35:44,890 --> 00:35:46,100
Yes, Father.

842
00:35:47,690 --> 00:35:48,580
Father, please.

843
00:35:59,930 --> 00:36:01,030
Thank you.

844
00:36:07,850 --> 00:36:08,690
Changsheng.

845
00:36:08,890 --> 00:36:10,160
Just now,

846
00:36:10,160 --> 00:36:11,580
you weren't even afraid of me.

847
00:36:12,290 --> 00:36:14,580
Why do you look scared

848
00:36:15,250 --> 00:36:16,300
of our Second Prince?

849
00:36:16,810 --> 00:36:17,650
Your Majesty.

850
00:36:18,250 --> 00:36:19,350
I'd better

851
00:36:20,080 --> 00:36:21,510
not tell you the reason.

852
00:36:22,810 --> 00:36:24,430
Since you said that,

853
00:36:25,080 --> 00:36:27,430
I must know the reason.

854
00:36:27,770 --> 00:36:29,180
I don't mean this.

855
00:36:29,850 --> 00:36:31,100
I'm just afraid that saying this

856
00:36:31,560 --> 00:36:33,220
will drive a wedge between you two.

857
00:36:33,560 --> 00:36:35,470
Then I'll become a sinner.

858
00:36:35,690 --> 00:36:36,530
You won't.

859
00:36:36,850 --> 00:36:37,870
I won't punish you.

860
00:37:01,310 --> 00:37:06,380
Sitting alone in the west window,
quietly watching the snow

861
00:37:07,910 --> 00:37:14,000
Silently falling and piling up

862
00:37:14,660 --> 00:37:20,830
The red flowers can't stand the cold

863
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:26,740
And withered at night

864
00:37:28,040 --> 00:37:33,310
Facing the freezing north wind

